h5. Problem description
When run on MobileWeb, confirm dialogs does not close after clicking on yes or no.

Reproducible with https://github.com/appcelerator/alloy/tree/master/test/apps/testing/ALOY-949 sample code or with:

index.js
{code}
var dialogs = require('alloy/dialogs');
$.index.open();
dialogs.confirm();
{code}

index.xml
{code}
<Alloy>
	<Window/>
</Alloy>
{code}

Result: nothing happens when clicking on the "No" or "Yes" Confirm dialog button on MobileWeb.

On Android and iOS it works as expected.

Not a regression
